div.data-content:
圆盘的动能

$$
\begin{alignat}{2}
&\text{平动:} T_t &&= \frac{1}{2} m (r \dot \theta_2)^2 \\
&\text{转动:} T_r &&= \frac{1}{2} J \dot \theta_2^2 \\
&&&= \frac{1}{2}(\frac{1}{2} m r^2) \dot \theta_2^2
\end{alignat}
$$

div.data-content:
杆的动能

$$
\begin{alignat}{2}
&\text{平动:} T_t &&= \frac{1}{2} m \left( (r \dot \theta _2- \frac{3}{2}r \dot \theta_1 \cos\theta_1)^2 + (\frac{3}{2}r \dot \theta_1 \sin \theta_1)^2 \right)\\
&\text{转动:} T_r &&= \frac{1}{2} J \dot \theta_1^2 \\
&&&= \frac{1}{2}(\frac{1}{12} m (2r)^2) \dot \theta_1^2
\end{alignat}
$$

div.data-content:
由Lagrange方程

$$\frac{{\rm{d}}}{{{\rm{d}}t}}\left( {\frac{{\partial L}}{{\partial {{\dot q}_i}}}} \right) - \frac{{\partial L}}{{\partial {q_i}}} = 0$$

代入得


$$
\begin{cases}
3mr^2\ddot{\theta}_1 - \frac{3}{2}mr^2\cos{\theta_1}\ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{3}{2}mr^2\sin{\theta_1}\dot{\theta}_1\dot{\theta}_2 - \frac{3}{2}mr^2\sin{\theta_1}\dot{\theta}_1\dot{\theta}_2 + \frac{3}{2}mgr\sin{\theta_1} = 0\\
\frac{5}{2}mr^2\ddot{\theta}_2 - \frac{3}{2}mr^2\cos{\theta_1}\ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{3}{2}mr^2\sin{\theta_1}\dot{\theta}_1^2 = 0
\end{cases}
$$
